      <task>
        <statement>
          <p>
            Let <m>A = (2,3)</m> and <m>B = (4,7)</m>, as shown at left in <xref ref="F-9-2-vector-magnitude-a" />. Compute <m>\Vert\overrightarrow{AB}\Vert</m>.
